/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180821/bkn-20180821115612633-0821_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180821%2Fbkn-20180821115612633-0821_00822_001.html&d=ogEaDYtAKoEXuTJTj9L6UpUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=6e1a8a16\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180821/bkn-20180821115612633-0821_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n公共專業聯盟膠鐵方案都唔太掂..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T08:27:35.000Z","msg":"港珠澳個島點起貨櫃碼頭？貨櫃船滿載廿幾層高架"}]}